OL,3,CMan charged after woman raped in
OL,4,CBristol
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith rape after a woman was attacked
OL,8,Fin Bristol.
OL,10,FAvon and Somerset Police said a woman
OL,11,Fwas raped in the Assembly Rooms Lane
OL,12,Farea at around 3.05am on Sunday 29
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,FNitesh Nitesh, of Byron Street in
OL,16,FRedfield, has been charged with one
OL,17,Fcount of rape.
OL,19,FHe's due to appear at Bristol
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court on Monday (6 April).
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
