OL,3,CMan charged after woman raped in
OL,4,CBristol
OL,6,FThe force said two other men arrested
OL,7,Fin connection with the investigation
OL,8,Fhave been released while enquiries
OL,9,Fcontinue.
OL,11,FDet Insp Simon Broad, from Avon and
OL,12,FSomerset Police, said: "We continue to
OL,13,Fsupport and update the victim on our
OL,14,Fprogress, and I would like to take
OL,15,Fthis opportunity to praise her for the
OL,16,Fstrength and courage she has
OL,17,Fdemonstrated throughout.
